	<div class="column">
		<h6>About us</h6>
		
		<p>We are a small but growing <b>family-like private nursery and primary school</b> offering a high-quality international education <b>in English</b> <!--to both Czech and international children -->with a particular emphasis on the development of international mindedness.</p>
		
    <p>As an international school, we follow specific standards that regulate our program and determine our curriculum. Our mission is to <b>help children learn better</b> and provide them with broad and balanced learning experience. <!--Something they will look back at with joy. --></p>
    
    <p>Our school is a proud member of <b>COBIS (Council of British International Schools)</b> and a registered <b>Cambridge International School</b> offering internationally recognized primary programmes and qualifications. The school is also a member of <b>IPC (International Primary Curriculum)</b> which is an exciting modern curriculum<!-- for the 21st century-->.</p>
